{"tid":2102672,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發][本土ACG創作] 香港本土ACG團隊與《榮光》作者合作，直衝日本市場","createTime":"2020-07-10T15:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T16:35:37.000Z","uid":168267,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"25a26ccb3f17042e7ce2939400eab2c4afc90af8","tid":2102672,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3LVH6y3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3LVH6y3.jpg&h=285c29ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"medium\"><span class=\"purple\">利申：非製作組成員，代冇acc嘅手足開post</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港係<strong>國際都市</strong>，可以<strong>自由汲取世界各國文化</strong>，自然都有能力創作各種文化嘅優秀作品。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;其中自然都有<strong>日本ACG文化愛好者嘅團隊</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n今次嘅陣容係：<strong>《榮光》作者DGX團隊 X 香港本土ACG團隊</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n呢次佢哋合作製作一個<br />\n<br />\n<strong>【21世紀の香港を舞台とする一つの想像の恋愛ストーリーを3、4分間にお見せする、独特の世界観を持つ日本語ボーカロイドMV作品です。】<br />\n以21世紀嘅香港為舞台，以3、4min時間展現虛構嘅戀愛story，世界觀獨特嘅純日文VocaloidMV作品。</strong><br />\n<br />\n而且呢個作品仲有<strong>「多層次嘅互動要素（「多重的インターアクション要素」）」</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n團隊啱啱喺日本最大型眾籌網站Campfire上發起<strong>眾籌</strong>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://camp-fire.jp/projects/view/304339\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcamp-fire.jp%2Fprojects%2Fview%2F304339&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumk2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=d0e0dbdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://camp-fire.jp/projects/view/304339</a><br />\n<br />\n咁今次呢個計劃除咗大家都識嘅<strong>DGX團隊</strong>提供優秀嘅音樂、編曲、混音之外。<br />\n<br />\n仲有<strong>香港本土知名畫師Mzcca</strong>負責角色設計（IG <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mzcca0.16/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmzcca0.16%2F&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumk2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=85547f4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/mzcca0.16/</a> ）。人設方案如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X0vpAr0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX0vpAr0.jpg&h=59202e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2FteXFj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FteXFj.jpg&h=42c1fa04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外有不願公開身份嘅畫師製作緊主視覺圖。草圖如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BYxO168.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBYxO168.jpg&h=90b2b8a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劇本、歌詞、世界觀設計由日本線手足 楊維理 負責，同時亦都係呢個計劃嘅召集人，<strong>日文水準係nativespeaker</strong>，至於本次計劃作品嘅內容為咗避免劇透暫時唔公開，但係呢度有一篇 用於描寫世界觀嘅超短篇日文小說《廃棄された二人だけの駅》，大家可以睇吓。<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/14wwFsj1bwqbFjPKiycitMt0qKARlJ0nUW3AZlL9nrro/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F14wwFsj1bwqbFjPKiycitMt0qKARlJ0nUW3AZlL9nrro%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumk2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=c934800a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/14wwFsj1bwqbFjPKiycitMt0qKARlJ0nUW3AZlL9nrro/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n而今次Project會用Vocaloid進行製作，所以都需要有人去進行電子音嘅調教，而負責嘅人係同為日本線手足嘅 貓有九個肝。試聽：<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1l0KUqDPFMNzly3x1OjpEfp6LUirODRMR/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1l0KUqDPFMNzly3x1OjpEfp6LUirODRMR%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumk2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=ee48aa83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1l0KUqDPFMNzly3x1OjpEfp6LUirODRMR/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n資金用途：<br />\n始終今次創作工作量頗大，花費時間亦都絕對唔係工餘時間可以解決，所以我哋都需要支付返相關報酬俾各位staff，始終冇可能叫大家用咁多時間做義工，所以都希望能夠俾返一份報酬比各位。<br />\n<strong>今次大家都係以低於市價嘅水準創作，但今次project嘅staff水準係音樂、文字、美術、設計等方面都睇得出能夠同日本行家一較高下</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n當然，我認為今次project亦都係<strong>文宣</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n我個人分析：過去一年日本線手足非常努力，但收效甚微<br />\n<br />\n我作為日本線一員，發現：<br />\n其實一般普通嘅日本人對於政治極其唔熱衷，更莫講話外國嘅嘢。直接進行表達、宣傳，基本無用，除非你係周庭BB。<br />\n<br />\n難得有成功嘅，日本線文宣想要成功就要咁：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.excite.co.jp/news/article/Bizjournal_202005_post_160139/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.excite.co.jp%2Fnews%2Farticle%2FBizjournal_202005_post_160139%2F&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumk2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=c3cec7d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.excite.co.jp/news/article/Bizjournal_202005_post_160139/</a><br />\n<br />\n幾萬轉發，而且被日本各大網站介紹。<br />\n<br />\n這條推特嘅大致內容是：指出香港人因為【國安法】將會失去自由玩【遊戲】嘅權利。<br />\n<br />\n成功原因有三點：<br />\n<strong>1、提到日本人也喜歡嘅事物&mdash;&mdash;遊戲<br />\n2、悲情，能夠引起同情心<br />\n3、真情實感</strong><br />\n<br />\n所以日本人就【感同身受】，自然而然咁關注<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋調返轉諗住製作一款<strong>符合日本人審美觀</strong>，能夠打動到佢哋嘅作品。一個<strong>講述&ldquo;香港嘅故事&rdquo;</strong>嘅fiction作品。<br />\n大家諗吓如果呢一個作品能夠引起日本人都覺得唔錯，覺得<strong>「お前ら日本人じゃないのに、こんな日本式の作品も作れるなんて...」&mdash;&mdash;「你哋唔係日本人，但能製作日式風格嘅優質作品...」</strong>，引起佢哋嘅關注，甚至可以喺<strong>網上引起一定迴響</strong>，進而從作品內容中理解今日香港嘅困境，然後再帶出<strong>「製作呢個作品嘅團隊，依家正正受到中國壓迫」</strong>呢個訊息，反而可能會令本身冇興趣嘅人會去關心香港。<br />\n<br />\n咁收咗錢冇可能咁冇交帶，計劃嘅進度我哋都會喺campfire、Twitter以及連登發布進展報告等等，大家可以隨時了解到計劃進度。<br />\n<br />\n另外，根據眾籌網站嘅要求，捐款嘅朋友我哋亦都<strong>準備咗一啲周邊當係回禮，以感謝各位手足嘅支持</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n PlanA<br />\n1000日元（70HKD）：<strong>片尾署名權</strong>+DGX嘅感謝信<br />\n<br />\nPlanB<br />\n2000日元（140HKD）：片尾署名權+DGX嘅感謝信+主視覺圖（PSD完整尺寸）+小說<br />\n<br />\nPlanC<br />\n5000日元（350HKD）：片尾署名權+DGX嘅感謝信+主視覺圖（PSD完整尺寸）+小說+所有繪畫素材+所有音聲素材<br />\n<br />\nPlanD<br />\n10000日元（700HKD）：片尾署名權+DGX嘅感謝信+主視覺圖（PSD完整尺寸）+小說+所有繪畫素材+所有音聲素材+Mzcca特別賀圖+公式解說書+向製作方進行一次提問嘅權利（不涉及私隱都可問）<br />\n<br />\n Campfire課金教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1lg_keHrz4jXU6WU6GL3GpQA4aRZYyN4F2vHU7TkTAjI/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1lg_keHrz4jXU6WU6GL3GpQA4aRZYyN4F2vHU7TkTAjI%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumk2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=81bf9294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1lg_keHrz4jXU6WU6GL3GpQA4aRZYyN4F2vHU7TkTAjI/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n唔使註冊都可以課金，非常方便，希望大家慷慨解囊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>最低1000日元，即可在&ldquo;DGX團隊X香港本土ACG團隊&rdquo;嘅作品最後署名，亦可支援日本線文宣。</strong><br />\n<br />\n如果有咩問題大家可以留言，都可以send email 去 <ins>aikahk20200625@gmail.com</ins> 今次眾籌等事項由本土ACG團隊 AiKaHK 負責。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G0CO176.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG0CO176.jpg&h=fa3d9208&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"313436e84b5214d649ea41939c5e1c2d631217c7","tid":2102672,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"77ac191037bf07410ce7b52ff04b46635e8557f4","tid":2102672,"uid":308041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1229852dd453f9c36df71dfadd69b1627fe1ca","tid":2102672,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T09:25:23.000Z","msg":"小小建議，最好開左twitter ac 宣傳下"},{"pid":"321951a3c8971ab55161fecf33649a8455d72e53","tid":2102672,"uid":141097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T09:35:13.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7204de33a19348e8cc9681a17374f682d2cfae19","tid":2102672,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T09:37:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e0957a5fe8fbf96d9f4f28a06106d9de61ac06f","tid":2102672,"uid":233009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T09:58:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"68cdb72847838fd3b8b55c2b8fbfbd6c9896e0ad","tid":2102672,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T10:44:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b43140cba16479ce4f9a867a2e66b4b7a235b8e","tid":2102672,"uid":308318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T17:14:35.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"868420751eb4fdbe0382d1e75ec34977c583a72a","tid":2102672,"uid":307978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"G持😭"}]}